      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AKINA DASH (1) failed to feature last start after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won by 2.5 lengths at this track (24.70) beating Wearing Levis in a Special conditions H on February 11. Tough to beat if on-song. DR. ULMA (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Sandown over 515m behind Paw Jasta (30.23) in a Mix 6/7. Was a winner prior to that. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Cannot be taken lightly. CARTMAN (4) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if he can recapture his solid win a few runs back, getting around Warragul over 400m in 22.74. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. NUCLEAR CODE (3) good strike-rate overall and must be included.",
